{
  "text": "Fgf-signaling modulators fgf8a Fgf-receptor ligand important for dorsal-and isthmic organizers. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] fgf17b Fgf-receptor ligand, with roles in early embryonic patterning. [CITATION_3] spry2 Negative feedback modulator of MAPK activation. [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] spry4 Negative feedback modulator of MAPK activation.",
